data.description: Looking for newer construction without the wait of the new build process? Conclude your search, HERE! With this 2021, DR Horton home in Riverbend at Cameron Heights on a corner lot! This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home features a spacious open concept with over 1500+ square feet of living space. This layout entails separate dining and living room spaces, perfect for hosting family and friends. The bedrooms are all featured on the left side of the home, a two car garage and a private lanai! Don't want the hassle of replacing and repairing? You can ease your mind of worry about the age of the home's systems, as they're all newer and very well maintained. Heading to work or out of town? This DR Horton Allex D model also includes smart home additions to make your life simplified with a press of a button! Convenience and comfort to control the front door lock, doorbell, touch screen control hub, front porch lights and Dot all included with the sale. With a very low HOA, including a community pool, playground and cabana-- this home is a MUST SEE! Easy access to 417/I4, the downtown Sanford area, Sanford airport and nearby grocery/convenience stores. Only 40 minutes from world renown Daytona Beach! Stop searching and schedule your showing today
